---
title: SuperQuick Euro-Inspired Chorizo Wraps with Creamy Feta Sauce and Sweet Pepper Spread
description: Meet our quick and easy version of 'cevapi,' a grilled meat wrap hailing from the Balkan region of Europe. Packed with green lettuce mix and creamy feta spread, it's every bit as filling as it is delicious!

